{"tid":1983164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國官員：政府已確定容許華為參與5G建設","createTime":"2020-04-21T15:35:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T16:20:44.000Z","uid":97944,"like":3,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0eea313d4bbde076e8eca820c0660cf88b1c68f8","tid":1983164,"uid":97944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T15:35:28.000Z","msg":"英國政府高層官員透露，英國政府已確定，容許中國電訊設備製造商華為，在英國建設5G電訊網絡中存有角色，但否認英國政府是改變決定。英國外交部常務次官麥克唐納向國會議員表示，政府決定容許華為繼續投資當地5G市場，但會有嚴格條件，又認為做法並非對華為重開市場，強調中國是英國非常重要的合作夥伴。<br />\n<br />\n英國政府在一月決定，容許華為參與非敏感部份的5G網絡建設，市場份額最多三成半。"},{"pid":"170fa5f6b1143e38c4d3c2eaa190b06eff9de78e","tid":1983164,"uid":97944,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T15:35:52.000Z","msg":"Source: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1282432&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1282432%26csid%3D261_367&d=ltyh5TmdzGcNJFTF%2BAmR8kBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=d3f2fa94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1282432&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"7c260e5dc9447df245b5ccf10bc982b604e28f99","tid":1983164,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T15:36:21.000Z","msg":"Only sunset <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9420d0479bcdc34df185d0778b3f6f751abebc4","tid":1983164,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T15:36:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504625-20200124.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504625-20200124.htm&d=ltyh5TmdzGcNJFTF%2BAmR8kBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=f1a288bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504625-20200124.htm&h=7bf88cb6\" data-auto-link 